{"tid":1944770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來有人喺沙嶺幫離開咗既手足整咗個紀念碑","createTime":"2020-03-26T15:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T16:01:49.000Z","uid":39484,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4e482ed6c347c92fb36b95a4878ce4564a50cc18","tid":1944770,"uid":39484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:21:21.000Z","msg":"#手足投稿 #沙嶺<br />\n岩岩入沙嶺獻花<br />\n發覺原來已經有手足入去起左個壇<br />\n各位有心人都盡量入黎表示下心意啦，岩岩送左第一朶花，希望可以keep住有人黎幫手換花啦<br />\n詳細位置我唔公開啦，有心既自己入黎搵下啦<br />\n附圖兩張<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HNaNuau.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHNaNuau.jpg&h=e8349645&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xRCL0hc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxRCL0hc.jpg&h=afdd7365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TWFxFhe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTWFxFhe.jpg&h=684b9a55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由2019年6月15日 第一單因為反送中而死既梁義士<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ndfhRz9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FndfhRz9.jpg&h=b3243744&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n到2020年3月26日為止 有我地熟識既 周梓樂 陳彥霖 <br />\n更多既係一單單<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CM1wV4Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCM1wV4Q.jpg&h=94093eb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死因無可疑既自殺案<br />\n見到有手足整咗個紀念碑比所有死去既手足<br />\n雖然係好簡單既紀念碑<br />\n但係都希望大家唔好忘記咁多位死去既手足<br />\n喺成功光復香港嗰日<br />\n再正式搵個地方 設墓去悼念所有義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由反送中開始到今日九個半月既時間<br />\n大家可能都會覺得攰 <br />\n但係請大家諗下<br />\n點解當初我地要行出嚟<br />\n點解話要光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71b6b8c57c2ddd173a732664c0e8c893310718c","tid":1944770,"uid":39484,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:22:15.000Z","msg":"承先賢之志 燃革命之火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dee33c43b903190a65cfd2fe296c242fa6c90357","tid":1944770,"uid":237300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:22:44.000Z","msg":"有心"},{"pid":"b8070bf3200a228e260cf83e171cd506590e1768","tid":1944770,"uid":39484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:23:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63df2314d34bd3642a85608d30c7cb222aa28e42","tid":1944770,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:24:31.000Z","msg":"低調"},{"pid":"0ba780c3e4a8af181928897abd00ff452e54858e","tid":1944770,"uid":264074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />低調啲"},{"pid":"7e47405c37810126f7f37382b3ff8d35ae18acec","tid":1944770,"uid":67006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4c38bd6f4eb42fae5a3aecc63909b2b2eff768","tid":1944770,"uid":126782,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:30:48.000Z","msg":"你爆出來又會有黑警去搞個墳架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f78cf3746e78b71bc3d597d6828ec85ea2266bd","tid":1944770,"uid":39484,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:31:44.000Z","msg":"btw 另外想講下 <br />\n可能好多人覺得靜咗好多<br />\n但係其實喺大家見到見唔到既地方<br />\n一直有班手足堅持咁去抗爭<br />\n有連儂場手足 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1071733?fbclid=IwAR3KRSGl8a07lJNK8r9C6ANilMCB6b6sW-hFMOf9nLAEtm0sbj2xrXGg_6w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1071733%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3KRSGl8a07lJNK8r9C6ANilMCB6b6sW-hFMOf9nLAEtm0sbj2xrXGg_6w&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR5B82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=99326d9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1071733%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3KRSGl8a07lJNK8r9C6ANilMCB6b6sW-hFMOf9nLAEtm0sbj2xrXGg_6w&h=31816774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1071733?fbclid=IwAR3KRSGl8a07lJNK8r9C6ANilMCB6b6sW-hFMOf9nLAEtm0sbj2xrXGg_6w</a><br />\n有twitter 戰線手足<br />\n有tvb 戰線手足<br />\n有街站手足<br />\n有各大繼續做緊既哨站 channel 手足<br />\n亦有班日日操fit 自己 準備自己既手足<br />\n革命一直都進行中<br />\n今日既準備 可能就係他日成功既重要因素<br />\n如果人人都放棄 咁就真係完架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa8a5dfe185aa8c66ad3940b0e9ed1f8703862d","tid":1944770,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:32:41.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n承先賢之志 燃革命之火"},{"pid":"550f3d360c70606250b039d53510952efdf4b066","tid":1944770,"uid":40422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:34:11.000Z","msg":"擺上連登轉頭又比人拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663247b92b030e4f5ca38c9a131bf5e8e3077b3a","tid":1944770,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:34:28.000Z","msg":"點解係「堂上」同最尾係「門」<br />\n旁邊兩邊都「光復香港時代革命」怪怪地<br />\n建議再整過<br />\n<br />\n同一定要開光個牌位同香爐"},{"pid":"d64e171d703bbbd0e651ef674b0977a8ad3046d1","tid":1944770,"uid":39484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7a4c38bd6f4eb42fae5a3aecc63909b2b2eff768","tid":1944770,"uid":126782,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:30:48.000Z","msg":"你爆出來又會有黑警去搞個墳架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:34:46.000Z","msg":"位手足都預咗放唔到幾多日既<br />\n佢都想引起各位手足一點點